  <name>FreeYourDisk</name>
  <summary>Safe disk cleanup utility</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      FreeYourDisk scans your disk and safely cleans temporary files, large
      files, stale git worktrees and developer caches, with a modern visual
      dashboard.
    </p>
    <p>
      Scans are read-only. Deletions are previewed (dry-run) and go to the
      recoverable trash by default; permanent deletion is an explicit opt-in.
      Actions that require administrator rights run through a minimal Polkit
      helper, so the interface never runs as root.
    </p>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">FreeYourDisk.desktop</launchable>

